CREATE TABLE sales_data (id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
            product_name VARCHAR(255),
            sale_date DATE,
            sale_amount DECIMAL(10, 2));

CREATE TABLE customers (customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
            customer_name VARCHAR(255),
            customer_email VARCHAR(255),
            customer_phone VARCHAR(15));

CREATE TABLE products (product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
            product_name VARCHAR(255),
            category VARCHAR(50),
            price DECIMAL(10, 2));

CREATE TABLE sales_representatives (rep_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
            rep_name VARCHAR(255),
            rep_email VARCHAR(255),
            region VARCHAR(50));

CREATE TABLE orders (order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
            customer_id UUID,
            product_id UUID,
            order_date DATE,
            quantity INT,
            total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2));
